<h2> Roles </h2>
The following roles can be assigned
<ul>
  <li>Public - Anyone can veiw the volcano database.</li>
  <li>Registerd Users - Anyone can sign up and register to use the additional on the fly analysis features.</li>
  <li>Collaborators - Registered users can request access to be come a Collaborators and add in observations.</li>
  <li>Admin - Can edit any page, approve edits, assign access to users, add new users, add new users.</li>
</ul>
